|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080305020111/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/7260393.stm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。3月，他代表達寧頓上陣了7場賽事，他的借用期在3月27日被延長至球季結束<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/d/darlington/7316620.stm
|title=Quakers seal deals for loan trio
|date=2008-03-27
|accessdate=2008-03-27
|publisher=BBC Sport
