|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080403034026/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/d/darlington/7316620.stm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>，兩天前他在以1-3的比分不敵前球會巴拉福特的賽事中上陣<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/7309357.stm
|title=Darlington 1-3 Bradford
|date=2008-03-29
|accessdate=2008-03-29
